The holiday is not always written with red numbers
In Hungary the law defines with accuracy the days that are written with red numbers in the calendar and it has already been converted in a generalized practice that about the holidays - that the anus that comes will be less - the working days are reorganized.
Not even in the UE or in North America are theholidays unitary.
The Hungarian laws do a difference between national holiday, holiday of State and festive days.
The festive days they fundamentally relate to religious holidays and historical ephemerides.
We celebrate the New Anus also: the last day of the old anus, as well as the first day of the new anus it is festive - the latter especially so that they can rest those that passed celebrating the old anus.
During all the anus we have eleven holidays written with red numbers in the calendar.
It is national holiday on the 15th of March in memory of the revolution of 1848 and on the 23rd of October, commemorative day of the revolution of 1956.
On 20 of August we celebrate the foundation of the State, the 1o of May the holiday of the work, we, the 1o and 2 o of November, we remember to our relatives and deceased friends.
Besides, in our country they are holidays of two days the Easter of Resurrection, the Pentecostés and Christmas.
According to the calendar, our state, national or religious holidays few times coincide with a weekend, because of that frequently itself does bridge when before or after the holiday there is a single working day.
In exchange for the weekends lengthened like this, during the previous Saturdays he can not absent itself from the work or from the school.
He is the working minister that it regulates in its specific decree when people have to work exactly in exchange for the directly previous or subsequent day to the holiday.
This legal norm is of obligatory fulfillment for all the employers and for its employees, as well as for the employees and civil servants.
It is not obligatory however for the companies and institutions of services that, due to its function, work uninterruptedly even during the festive days.
This anus the working order will be able to be altered only around the holidays of the end of anus: from the 24 of December practically the life is stopped in the country, since according to the experiences, the majority of the people "it does bridge" during the days between Christmas and the end of the anus or take its holidays during these days.
The next anus several of our holidays will coincide with mediated or with weekends, for what there will be less changes in the working days than this anus.
First the agenda will be modified about the holiday of the work so that afterwards, for four successive days, the workers can rest.
On Saturday, 26 of April will be working day, for that in exchange on Friday 2 of May is festive day.
The other change is related to the holiday of the 23rd of October: on Saturday the 18th of October, people will have to work instead of Friday the 24th.
However, the anus that comes during the holiday of end of anus will be able to be rested, since from the 24th of December it will not be worked almost in any part, nor even if the last day of the anus it is a Wednesday.
