The premium is the price of the insurance, which is established taking into account different factors, such as the age, the sex, the antiquity of the card, the marital state, the type of vehicle to assure or the use that itself him of to this, among others.
The insurance companies establish its prices according to the statistics, so that to bigger probability of suffering an accident, bigger fee to pay.
