Likewise, resorting to the counting, the companies have arrived to the conclusion that the married people tend to have less accidents than the single drivers.
The use that itself him of to the vehicle will influence in the frequency, and with that in the probability of having some type of mishap.
When increasing the frequency they increase the probabilities.
The variables that the insurance companies take into account at the time of establishing the price of the premium are many.
